public interface PontoMarcacoes
extends PontoMarcacoesModel, com.liferay.portal.kernel.model.PersistedModel
    The extended model interface for the PontoMarcacoes service. Represents a row in the "ponto_marcacao" database table, with each column mapped to a property of this class.
